Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:01.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,580)\fad(500,0)\blur4}第3话 「与迪奥度过的青春」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0010,,我拿到解毒剂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才让爸爸喝下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 我的心情很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在竟然要将形同兄弟的你扭送警局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 你大概接受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这确实是我的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心意 确实是你善良的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 我有个请求 虽然这很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能给我点时间 让我去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才还在防备着他 以为他会像走投无路的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时准备反击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然平安从那贫民窟回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能实施那计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让他放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看准机会一口气用小刀干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很后悔 对以前走过的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为生在一个贫穷的环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中就怀着无意义的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会做出这样的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想毒害养育自己的恩人 抢夺他的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示我的悔意 我回来自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我要逃亡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国也好别的地方也好 都没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确…确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想赎罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要相信这家伙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一脸“你谁啊”的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先来自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱管闲事的史比特瓦根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为担心乔斯达先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从伦敦贫民窟一直跟到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 我喜欢你的天真 所以给你个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生在黑暗街 长在黑暗街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见过无数的恶党
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以凭味道就能分辨坏人和好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呕吐物还难闻的味道扑鼻而来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还从没见过这样的邪恶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环境所逼才当坏人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了！这人是天生的邪恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得这个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从这个东洋人口中得到卖给你毒药的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你倾注了不下于亲儿子的爱情和期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你还要静养的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回寝室休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到自己的儿子被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 接下来的事就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人不会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵上的三颗痣 以及他的脸相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是天生的强运者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 至少希望你能亲手给我扣上手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我们七年交情的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的能力真是有极限的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我短暂的人生里学到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人越是玩弄阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就越会在预料之外的事态失足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为超越人类的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子…不做人了！JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石面具！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在你那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射杀他！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 用你的鲜血啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一把小刀 一般情况是能避开的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却被石面具吸引了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而您就替我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…去世的妈妈的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一刀刺中要害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我来了还发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达卿 我早就跟他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如当时我将迪奥·布朗度的父亲放流荒岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥·布朗度的父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当上警察没多久的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住了一个想拿那颗戒指去抵押的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是迪奥的父亲 达利奥·布朗度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是我的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟妻子一对的结婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就被那个叫布朗度小偷抵押了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗度？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗度是乔斯达卿的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个对马车事故幸灾乐祸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机打劫财物的狡猾的恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戒指是我送给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是弥天大谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戒指是我送给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是无辜的 请释放了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么替他圆谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我也出身贫困 也许会做出跟他一样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去卖掉 为家人买点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再当坏人 要当个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达卿是在知道一切内情的情况下收养迪奥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生来了就会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 不要恨迪奥 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的亲生儿子 所以对你格外的严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迪奥看来 也许这反而是一种歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才会做出这样的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将迪奥安葬在布朗度先生的墓旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有遗憾了 JoJo 能死在儿子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怀抱里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的善良却带来如此的不幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收养迪奥是做错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样死了就毫无意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位父亲的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他的儿子乔纳森·乔斯达全部继承下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会成为他的强大意志 自豪和未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说 我最讨厌那种一遇到挫折就痛哭的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这对父子不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不为自己所做的事情后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是最可爱最天真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸…尸体…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥·布朗度的尸体不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生 快躲离窗户！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========B Part========
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官的头被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这家伙复活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 中了那么多枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 他肯定拿着什么武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 快开枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪…迪奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊 JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开枪！开枪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打中了头部的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 我完全不知道发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到如此强大的力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石面具赐予的！是你父亲的血赐予的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UUUURRRRYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吸取人类的精气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥究竟成为了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大脑中异常的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀刺…父亲的死…血…迪奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石面具…研究记录…大脑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的能力…未知的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥已经不是人类了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UURRYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打不过他的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过那样的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没见过能超越那股力量的魔物！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 实话说我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 迪奥 不能让你留在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的责任 我要收拾你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑！肯定是石面具的骨针
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大脑激发了人类的潜藏能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 打倒迪奥的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸…尸体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热热的血…我要喝血！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸到血就行了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对手是怪物 但还是很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 请给予我更强大的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要更强大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥已经不是人类 是魔物了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让迪奥继续增加杀戮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡…挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中将他刺穿挡住了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 他头部的伤口愈合了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身！完全的不死身！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫弱啊 贫弱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jo——Jo！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再玩一会 再让我用这股美妙的力量玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也还不知道能有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是玩弄计谋就越会失足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做无谓挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别光躲在窗帘后面打颤 出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是计谋 是勇气！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织在被烧焦的同时再生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这个才是不死之身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点火不能打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 史比特瓦根！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来是无关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能往上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势会往整座宅邸蔓延的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来啊 迪奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥！不能让你和你的力量放进人世！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我的注意力从同伴身上引开？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成全你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的烧伤 就吸取你的血来治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用 没用 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点高度 我跳下去也毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反 被火势和高度逼得无路可走的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 您安息吧 请在这场大火中前往天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将力量赋予火焰 助我成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生 你究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…难道你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能那样做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URRRRRRY！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫弱啊 贫弱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间 JoJo的大脑里闪过自己的一幕幕青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的青春 是跟迪奥一起度过的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就来为我的青春做个了结！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让火势来得更猛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要火势大到超越那魔物的回复力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能打倒迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此他爬到屋顶等待火势烧遍整座宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢打这样的主意！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祖先代代生活的乔斯达邸正在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲死了 我一无所有 失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这条命！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条性命也一并燃烧吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代价 迪奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要封印你的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Bye JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一瞬间 我实在为你的觉悟震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父亲的尸体旁 流着欢喜的泪水死去吧 蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超越人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身 不老不死 我能支配这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 这是你给我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥！我回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我不会松手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 你的命数尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把刀…这把刀是你刺死爸爸的刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双臂的骨头都碎了 身上都着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是力量没有减小丝毫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好 我们一起投入烈火中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 死的只会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论火势有多大 还是应该有能逃出去的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！给予我最后的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼叫 忘情的吼叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼叫的声音传达给父亲的灵魂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是无意中利用了从小长大的府邸的构造吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹬墙了！蹬过去的方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达家的守护神 慈爱的女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…你这混蛋竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那从小就不容小觑的爆发力！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生…不应该…这样结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔斯达先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
